obj_root_law_sections_1:
  sectionId (68316)
  sectionNo (1)
  orderNo 1
  title `Short title.`
  content obj_root_law_sections_1_content
  footnotes obj_root_law_sections_1_footnotes
  query abv=CEN&statehandle=123456789/1362&actid=AC_CEN_5_5_00099_187917_1663829896037&sectionId=68316&sectionno=1&orderno=1&orgactid=AC_CEN_5_5_00099_187917_1663829896037
obj_root_law_sections_1_content:
  string
  line `This Act may be cited as the ^1Dekkhan Agriculturists' Relief Act, 1879: and`
  line
  line `Commencement.--it shall come into force on the first day of November, 1879.`
  line
  line `Local extent.-- ^2[This section and]`
  line `except ^4[the territories which, immediately before the 1st November, 1956, were comprised in Part`
  line `B States]]. The rest of this Act ^5extends only to the districts of Poona, Satara, Sholapur and`
  line `Ahmednagar ^6[but may, from time to time, be extended wholly or in part by the State`
  line `Government ^7*** to any other district or districts in the ^8[territories which, immediately before the`
  line `1st November, 1956, were comprised in the State of Bombay,]]`
  line `^9[or to any part or parts of any`
  line `other such district or districts].`
obj_root_law_sections_1_footnotes:
  string
  line `1. Acts 17 of 1879, 23 of 1881 and 22 of 1882 may be cited collectively as the Dekkhan Agriculturists' Relief Acts, 1879 to 1882--`
  line `see s. 1(1) of the Dekkhan Agriculturists' Relief Act, 1882 (22 of 1882). The Acts of 1879 to 1882 and Act 23 of 1886 may be`
  line `cited collectively as the Dekkhan Agriculturists' Relief Acts, 1879 to 1886--see s. 1(1) of the Dekkhan Agriculturists' Relief`
  line `Act, 1886 (23 of 1886). The Acts of 1879 to 1886 and Act 6 of 1895 may be cited collectively as the Dekkhan Agriculturists'`
  line `Relief Acts, 1879 to 1895--see s. 1(1) of the Dekkhan Agriculturists' Relief Act, 1895 (6 of 1895). The Acts of 1879 to 1895`
  line `and Bom. Act 1 of 1902 may be cited collectively as the Dekkhan Agriculturists' Relief Acts, 1876 to 1902--see s. 1(1) of the`
  line `Dekkhan Agriculturists' Relief Act, 1902 (Bom. 1 of 1902).`
  line
  line `2. These words were inserted by Act 23 of 1881, Section 3, and are to be deemed to have always been inserted.`
  line
  line `3. Subs. by the A.O. 1950, for "all the Provinces of India".`
  line `4. Subs by the A.L.O., 1956 for "Part B States".`
  line
  line `5. The Act was repealed in the State of Bombay, with effect from 27-5-1950 by the Bombay Agricultural Debtors' Relief Act, 1947`
  line `Bom. 28 of 1947), s. 56 as amended. Hence the part applicable to that State only has not been reproduced.`
  line
  line `6. Ins. by Act 23 of 1886, s. 3.`
  line
  line `7. The words "with the previous sanction of the G.G. in C." rep. by Act 38 of 1920, s. 2 and Schedule I.`
  line
  line `8. Subs. by 2 A.L.O., 1956 , for "State of Bombay" (w.e.f. 1-11-1956).`
  line
  line `9. Ins. by Act 23 of 1886, s. 3.`
